
File list
----------

   README

   modules/

   	LayoutTranspose.chpl	transpose domain map
   	LayoutCA.chpl		CA domain map 

   examples/
        
	trans_ex0.chpl     basic use of transposed array 
	trans_ex1.chpl     basic use of transposed array of strings
	trans_ex2.chpl     matrix copy from RMO to CMO 
                           (includes code for GPU but not functional)
	trans_ex4.chpl     matrix multiply with transposed

	ca_ex0.chpl        basic use of CA tranformed array 
	ca_ex1.chpl        basic use of CA transformed array of strings
	ca_ex2.chpl        matrix copy from RMO to CA 
                           (includes code for GPU but not functional)
	ca_ex3.chpl        multiple CA arrays with different tiles sizes
	ca_ex4.chpl        matrix multiply with CA

     
 
To run examples 
---------------

    1. Place Layout*.chpl in a module search directory (e.g., pwd or
       ${CHPL_HOME}/modules/layouts). Alternatively, create symbolic links to
       these files from a module search directory.  

    2. Build examples

         cd examples 
         chpl -o ca --set chpl_dl_validate=true ca_ex0.chpl

       To suppress validation results, omit the chpl_dl_validate flag. 

    3. Execute  
  
          ./ca
	  

